s. <br> <p></p><span class="SignatureTitle">-----signature-----</span><div class="SignatureText">Midgard Galahad <br>  <br> </div></td></tr><tr align="right" valign="bottom"><td colspan=2 class="BoardRowB"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/post.asp?brd=5176&topic=85711421">Post Reply</a> | <a href="/active_topic_notify.asp?mes=85759176" class="BoardRowBLink">Active Topic Notification</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/pm_send.asp?usr=453520">Private Message</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/user_posts.asp?usr=453520">Post History</a></td></tr><tr align="left" valign="top" class="BoardRowA"><td class="BoardRowA" rowspan=3 width="17%"><a href=" http://users.ign.com/about/ArkadyTepes?boards=vn " class="AuthorLink">ArkadyTepes</a>&nbsp;<a href="/Help/Faqs.aspx#stars"><img align=absmiddle src=/images/star4.gif border=0 hspace=0 vspace=0 alt="1,297 posts"></a><br><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><!-- WISH & COLL STUFF --><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr class="BoardRowA"><td nowrap="false" class="BoardRowA"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="http://users.ign.com/collection/ArkadyTepes"><font size="1">collection (56)</font></a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="http://users.ign.com/wishlist/ArkadyTepes"><font size="1">wishlist (7)</font></a></td></tr></table><!-- /WISH & COLL STUFF	--><span style="font-weight: bold;">Posts:</span> 1,297<br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Registered:</span> Jan 04<br></span><br></td><td class="BoardRowA" colspan=2 width="83%"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Date Posted:</span>&nbsp;4/19 8:46am&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bold;">Subject:</span> RE: RADARING ISSUE FIX</td></tr><tr valign=top><td class="BoardRowB" colspan=2 width="83%">the bandwidth used for this game is very minimal <br>  <br> see they send you information for who's in the realm. <br> so the client ques and preloads/caches the graphics its gunna need. <br> then they enter clip range. and it displays them <br>  <br> without the information of the zone.. there not preloaded/cached..   so it takes longer for the client to dig them up thus creating more video lag. <br>  <br>  <br> this is known to work.. because the client used to allow you to preload ALL information.. but they removed that option with the catacombs engine. and with it all preloaded i never had lag when people entered clip range.. now i have a short stutter as people hit clip range.. its extremely annoying that they took out the option.  <br> <p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr align="right" valign="bottom"><td colspan=2 class="BoardRowB"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/post.asp?brd=5176&topic=85711421">Post Reply</a> | <a href="/active_topic_notify.asp?mes=85775216" class="BoardRowBLink">Active Topic Notification</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/pm_send.asp?usr=879976">Private Message</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/user_posts.asp?usr=879976">Post History</a></td></tr><tr align="left" valign="top" class="BoardRowA"><td class="BoardRowA" rowspan=3 width="17%"><a href=" http://users.ign.com/about/Katt.?boards=vn " class="AuthorLink">Katt.</a>&nbsp;<a href="/Help/Faqs.aspx#stars"><img align=absmiddle src=/images/star5.gif border=0 hspace=0 vspace=0 alt="5,479 posts"></a><br><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><!-- WISH & COLL STUFF --><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr class="BoardRowA"><td nowrap="false" class="BoardRowA"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="http://users.ign.com/collection/Katt."><font size="1">collection (1)</font></a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="http://users.ign.com/wishlist/Katt."><font size="1">wishlist (0)</font></a></td></tr></table><!-- /WISH & COLL STUFF	--><span style="font-weight: bold;">Posts:</span> 5,479<br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Registered:</span> Nov 01<br></span><br></td><td class="BoardRowA" colspan=2 width="83%"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Date Posted:</span>&nbsp;4/19 9:00am&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bold;">Subject:</span> RE: RADARING ISSUE FIX</td></tr><tr valign=top><t